{"id": "1251877130774773780", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "332142766962245633", "author_name": "alanhsu100", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T12:32:46.729000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1251877130594156646", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-16-19-13-18-477_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 126760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1251366410475536515/1251877130594156646/Screenshot_2024-06-16-19-13-18-477_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=69cbbeee&is=69ca6d6e&hm=eca6e1311105a12268fd04bac46ccfe93e3db4b2c41d6357b65de8689b222da5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251877392599879763", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "332142766962245633", "author_name": "alanhsu100", "author_bot": false, "content": "圖片是不是不能新加阿...", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T12:33:49.153000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251945480758366278", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "关于第2关，如果手法不够好，我个人建议是用深海界域以外的队伍打。", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:04:22.635000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251945774095401060", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "因为这一关不能用掉狂乱刷诅咒造物，也没有精英怪可以凹出苦痛圣腕。", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:05:32.572000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251946114542735390", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "另外，如果单回合爆发不够，打掉BOSS之后，会分裂出两个血很多的小怪。深海较为的平均输出能力也恰好被这个【分裂】机制所克制。", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:06:53.741000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251946556974956545", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "同时，如果墨菲的启灵不够，3费牌没有保留，很可能会出现爆发回合没有手段刻上【易伤】的情况，即使用了灵摆，复制墨菲两张3费，也很难解决【易伤】问题。", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:08:39.225000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251946731076190291", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "当然，如果会玩水母就解决了（可是好多人不会小水母唉）<:hello:1236949723949174865>", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:09:20.734000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:09:44.568000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251947706281230396", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "还有，关于第5关，地图右下角的【融蚀疯马】的那个战斗可以放掉，因为难度有点大，不如保血量打艾继丝。5-3的疯马两回合可以踹你800左右的血量。", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:13:13.241000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1251950131629133854", "channel_id": "1251366410475536515", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "有点话多了，给楼主薯条🍟", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T17:22:51.489000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1251366410475536515", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1252048517099159653", "channel_id": "1237818165472264242", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181985385564360854", "author_name": "linuk0460", "author_bot": false, "content": "总之是趁米粒落地前把债还上了<:flop:1243504846062223360> \n新增深海国家队运营思路与实战教学，虽然几个小时后弥妈就要落地但是总体思路变化应该不大，可以作为参考使用。", "timestamp": "2024-06-16T23:53:48.413000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1252048516784590980", "filename": "v1.0.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 5234246, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1237818165472264242/1252048516784590980/v1.0.pdf?ex=69cbb5cc&is=69ca644c&hm=d86e14dbb57114532e98cd6f9768ba978aeb83192d9bddddd4728a8e88de29ae&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1237818165472264242", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "守密人战斗指导手册v0.8", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130"]}
